Headline: #Mahindra Last Mile Mobility Launches ZEO Electric 4W SCV Starting at ‚Çπ7.52 Lakh

Summary: Mahindra Last Mile Mobility has unveiled the Mahindra ZEO, India's first electric 4-wheeler designed for urban logistics, priced from ‚Çπ7.52 lakh.
